Yui: [SIGH, INTAKE OF BREATH]

77
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:47,805
Thank you for coming today, Miss.

78
00:05:51,017 --> 00:05:53,186
Announcer: The train is now
approaching the station.

79
00:05:53,353 --> 00:05:57,440
[GASPS] I know, you don't
have to tell me, I'm late.

80
00:05:57,523 --> 00:06:00,485
- Sorry.
- Lightning: No tails?

81
00:06:00,651 --> 00:06:03,029
Mmm.

82
00:06:03,404 --> 00:06:05,758
- [INTERCOM BEEP]
- Background: Yes, ma'am. Traffic control.

83
00:06:05,782 --> 00:06:09,869
Hello, Traffic Center.
How may I help you?

84
00:06:10,036 --> 00:06:14,499
Yui: Umm... I just saw the suspect in the
Tomomi Murashita murder case.

85
00:06:14,665 --> 00:06:18,669
- Yes... On East Kichijoji Street, huh?
- Uh huh.

86
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:22,465
Next to the big parking lot. Right.
Thanks for your help.

87
00:06:32,183 --> 00:06:33,893
Hey! What're you doing?

88
00:06:33,976 --> 00:06:36,646
[GASPS] Shogo Yahagi!

89
00:06:36,813 --> 00:06:38,689
No! Wait! For god's sake,
don't shoot!

90
00:06:38,856 --> 00:06:42,026
- [AIRSOFT GUN SHOTS]
- [SCREAMS AND WHIMPERS]

91
00:06:42,193 --> 00:06:44,404
- So long, sucker!
- [BOUNCY ACTION MUSIC]

92
00:06:49,617 --> 00:06:51,786
