94
00:07:17,895 --> 00:07:20,314
- Comin' through!
- [SHOPPER SCREAMS]

95
00:07:28,739 --> 00:07:31,367
Moron! What the hell
were you thinking?!

96
00:07:31,534 --> 00:07:34,972
- Megaphone Cop: Take care of all the exits!
Don't let him get out of there! - Yes, sir!

97
00:07:34,996 --> 00:07:36,998
Gangway!

98
00:07:58,603 --> 00:08:01,898
What an idiot.
That's a dead end.

99
00:08:23,711 --> 00:08:26,130
- [MUSIC STOPS]
- [SCOFFS]

100
00:08:27,465 --> 00:08:29,008
Heh!

101
00:08:31,135 --> 00:08:33,012
Let's rock!

102
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:36,010
Jacket: \"Kumi For Life\"
[BOUNCY ACTION MUSIC RESUMES]

103
