01:17:23,930 --> 01:17:31,897
I tried calling out your name.

944
01:17:31,980 --> 01:17:39,980
Somewhere inside me,
someone else is there.

945
01:17:43,533 --> 01:17:51,533
- What can the two of us do for love?
