reasons for it.

960
01:19:36,104 --> 01:19:39,649
Lonely sunset...

961
01:19:39,733 --> 01:19:43,528
I'm afraid to weep.
(Afraid)

962
01:19:43,612 --> 01:19:47,115
Lonely sunset...

963
01:19:47,199 --> 01:19:52,662
I'm so scared, it's so hard.
(Hard)

964
01:19:52,746 --> 01:19:56,458
